OL,6,F"The illegal sale of such items not
OL,7,Fonly has health implications but also
OL,8,Fhas associated anti-social behaviour
OL,9,Fand criminality.
OL,11,F"The Closure Notice is another step in
OL,12,Four continued plan to improve the
OL,13,Fquality of life for the residents of
OL,14,FAdamsdown. Our partnership approach to
OL,15,Fthe area is heralding positive results
OL,16,Fin targeting criminality and we have
OL,17,Fplenty more to give."
