OL,6,FA spokesperson for Shared Regulatory
OL,7,FServices said: "Illegal tobacco does
OL,8,Fgreat harm in the community. Its
OL,9,Fcheapness and ease of supply are
OL,10,Fparticularly attractive to young
OL,11,Fpeople and others on lower incomes,
OL,12,Fand it eliminates the price incentive
OL,13,Ffor existing smokers to quit the habit.
OL,15,F"I'm delighted to see this action
OL,16,Fbeing taken. Offenders need to know
OL,17,Fthat they will face consequences if
OL,18,Fthey choose to deal in these illegal
OL,19,Fproducts."
